-- Spain's Caixabank sees drop in credit stabilising towards end-2015
-- 
-- Fri Oct 24, 2014 04:34AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, Oct 24 (Reuters) - Caixabank <CABK.MC> Chief Executive Officer Gonzalo Gortazar on Friday said a drop in its overall lending to companies and families would stabilise towards the end of next year.

"It seems that the drop in lending will continue... We hope that it will stabilise towards the end of 2015," Gortazar told a press conference.